column26: Replace Amber Heard's Mera with Johnny Depp for Aquaman 2
column33: Warner Brothers: Replace Amber Heard's Mera with Johnny Depp for Aquaman 2
column34:
We've all heard the news about Amber Heard; she lied to us, the fans, while almost railroading the career of a beloved actor by fabricating allegations of domestic abuse. What should be done in wake of these fabricated stories? What would happen if we regular people would make something like this up? There would be consequences such as jail time, and most likely be fired and replaced. So why not do the same to Heard? And to rub salt in the wound, replace her with the person SHE had abused; Johnny Depp. Facial hair and all. Why not? And have no one acknowledge anything. "New haircut?" Sure. We all love Johnny.  

Let's show everyone that there can be consequences for everyone when they fabricate lies that impact people's lives, even if they are a movie star. PLUS; Have you seen Johnny Depp's acting range? Come on. COME ON.
